# README Language Rule

- Write and maintain the top-level `README.md` in Chinese.
- Command names, paths, environment variables, code identifiers, table headers, and unavoidable proper nouns may remain in English.
- When updating `README.md`, prefer concise Chinese explanations and avoid mixing large English prose sections into the document.
